1998;;The Man with Rain in His Shoes;;British;;María Ripoll;;Lena Headey, Douglas Henshall, Penélope Cruz;;rom com;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Man_with_Rain_in_His_Shoes;;Victor (Henshall) is an actor in London who is desperate to stop his ex-girlfriend, Sylvia (Headey), to whom he was unfaithful, from marrying another man. After meeting two mysterious dustmen, he is given the chance to travel back in time and relive his romance. However, he finds that things develop differently this time around—Sylvia has an affair with Dave (Strong), and she leaves him.